HEROES.

@USCG personnel rescued 8 people in Santa Cruz after they were trapped in a cave by rising tides.

The extraordinary bravery and selfless service of these Coast Guard heroes embody the best of what it means to be an American. https://t.co/xQBjYKaxCs

